		<p span style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:25px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><b>THINGS TO DO IN THE FIRST DAYS:</b></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:25px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><b>1 - CREATE A COMPANY:</b></span></span></p>

		<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><img  style="border: 4px solid #000" style="border: 4px solid #000" alt="Crie uma Empresa" src="../wiki_img/create_company.png"   /></span></span></p>
		
		<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em">You can use the goods and products you received to create a new company and post job openings so that your workers can work and you can start generating wealth.</span></span></p>
		<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em">Escolha uma empresa. Para cada tipo de empresa, você precisará de de alguns produtos para a sua construção. VocÊ pode ver quantos produtos são necessários e quantos produtos você tem.  </span></span></p>
		<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><strong>Exemplo:</strong></span></span></p>
		<ol>
			<li><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><strong>Sand Career: </strong> Type of Company.</span></span></li>
			<li><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><strong>Sand: </strong> Product that will be produced.</span></span></li>
			<li><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><strong>0.25 Gold: </strong> It is the amount of tax paid to the Government to create the company.</span></span></li>
			<li><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><strong>(Req/Avail): </strong> If you don't have enough in your Stock, it will appear in red.</span></span></li>
		</ol>
		
<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><img  style="border: 4px solid #000" style="border: 4px solid #000" alt="Escolha a Empresa" src="../wiki_img/choose_company.png" /> </span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><strong>2 - LAUNCH AND ACCEPT JOB OFFERS:</strong></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em">After founding the company you can post job offers. But before that, we advise you to expand your company to level 3. Just go to "UPGRADE" and go up to level 2 and then again "UPGRADE" to level 3. (Up to this level you have resources you gained when starting the game ).</span></span></p>

		<ol>
			<li><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><strong>Skill: </strong> It is the minimum level of the worker. To start, the ideal is to leave 1 to make it easier.</span></span></li>
			<li><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><strong>Saláry: </strong>It is the salary offered for the job. The minimum is 1 (local currency) for a working day.</span></span></li>
			<li><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><strong>Quantity: </strong>It's the number of vacancies. At level 1, you can cast 1 wave. Two vacancies at level 2 and 3 at level 3. You can upgrade your company to level 5.</span></span></li>
			<li><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><strong> OFFER: </strong>After choosing Skill, Salary and Quantity confirm by pressing "Offer".</span></span></li>
			<li><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><strong>OFFERED: </strong> After offering the vacancies, you can go to "Offered" and see the offers offered and already choose which workers will accept these offers. Just click on "Apply" and choose the worker who will accept the proposal.</span></span></li>
		</ol>
<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><img  style="border: 4px solid #000;height:500px" style="border: 4px solid #000" alt="Administrar a Empresa" src="../wiki_img/manage_company.png" /> </span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><strong>3 - INVEST RAW MATERIALS IN THE COMPANY:</strong></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em">Before starting work, it is necessary to invest resources in the company so that its workers can generate products.</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em">Each company needs different raw materials to work with.</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><strong>Example:</strong>Sand Company will need Energy.</span></span></p>


<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><img  style="border: 4px solid #000;height:500px" alt="Administrar a Empresa" src="../wiki_img/manage_company2.png"  /> </span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:25px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><b>4 - WORK:</b></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em">After launching the job offers and accepting them, the next step is to WORK.</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em">Just go to the ECONOMY menu >> WORK.</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em">On the page<strong>WORK</strong>, to make workers work just click "Work All".</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><img  style="border: 4px solid #000;height:400px" alt="Trabalhando" src="../wiki_img/work_all.png"/> </span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:25px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><b>5 - FIGHT IN DAILY BATTLES:</b></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em">The <strong>vMundus</strong> it is a place where at any moment a war can break out. And if your nation is involved in some war, you can and must help. </span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em">But if your nation is not directly linked to a conflict, you can still look for a Battle where the <strong>Aliens</strong> are involved. They are the only enemies in momum from all countries and you can fight any war against the <strong>Aliens</strong>.Damage against <strong>Aliens</strong> will earn you double experience. </span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><img  style="border: 4px solid #000" alt="Escolha a Batalha" src="../wiki_img/fight_choose.png"  /> </span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:25px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><b>6 - COLLECT THE DAILY TASKS BONUS:</b></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em">On the User Panel (Left Side of the Game) you can collect the daily bonuses for "WORK" and for "FIGHT".</span></span></p>


<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><img  style="border: 4px solid #000" alt="Missões Diárias" src="../wiki_img/daily_missions.png"  /> </span></span></p>
<ol>
			<li><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><strong>WORK: </strong> It's the daily bonus for working. If 2 workers work in the day, you can already collect the bonus of 4 Foods and 3 Extra Experience Points. Having up to 5 bonus levels to receive.</span></span></li>
			<li><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><strong>FIGHT: </strong>It is the daily bonus for fighting battles. If you add 200 damage points for the day, you can already collect the bonus of 8 Bullets (Ammo) and 3 Extra Experience Points. Having up to 5 bonus levels to receive.</span></span></li>
		</ol>
<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="line-height:1.5em"><img style="border: 4px solid #000; height:400px"  alt="Recolher Bônus" src="../wiki_img/daily_missions2.png" style="height:400px" /> </span></span></p>
		

